$h3 Custom License Validation

This example adds 
`keyGenLicenseValidationClass=com.company.product.keygen.CustomLicenseValidation`,
`keyGenLicenseValidationFunction=both`,
`keyMgrLicenseValidationClass=com.company.product.keymgr.CustomLicenseValidation` and
`keyMgrLicenseValidationFunction=both` to the basic configuration example in 
order to decorate the basic license validation in the Key Generator and Key 
Manager modules with custom functions.

    ${dollar} mvn archetype:generate -B \
        -DarchetypeArtifactId=$project.artifactId \
        -DarchetypeGroupId=$project.groupId \
        -DarchetypeVersion=$project.version \
        -DartifactId=license \
        -DcompanyName="Company Inc." \
        -DdefaultPassword=test1234 \
        -DgroupId=com.company.product \
        -DkeyGenLicenseValidationClass=com.company.product.keygen.CustomLicenseValidation \
        -DkeyGenLicenseValidationFunction=both \
        -DkeyMgrLicenseValidationClass=com.company.product.keymgr.CustomLicenseValidation \
        -DkeyMgrLicenseValidationFunction=both \
        -DlicensingSubject="Product 1" \
        -Dversion=1.0-SNAPSHOT
    [...]

