        -DarchetypeGroupId=$project.groupId \
        -DarchetypeVersion=$project.version \
        -DartifactId=license \
        -DcompanyName="Company Inc." \
        -DdefaultPassword=test1234 \
        -DgroupId=com.company.product \
        -DkeyMgrClockClass=com.company.product.keymgr.CustomClock \
        -DlicensingSubject="Product 1" \
        -Dversion=1.0-SNAPSHOT
    [...]

$h3 V2/XML License Key Format

This example adds `licenseKeyFormat=V2/XML` to the basic configuration example
in order to use the V2/XML license key format and remove the dependency on the
Jackson JSON Processor from the generated code.

    ${dollar} mvn archetype:generate -B \
        -DarchetypeArtifactId=$project.artifactId \
        -DarchetypeGroupId=$project.groupId \
        -DarchetypeVersion=$project.version \
        -DartifactId=license \
        -DcompanyName="Company Inc." \
        -DdefaultPassword=test1234 \
        -DgroupId=com.company.product \
        -DlicenseKeyFormat=V2/XML \
        -DlicensingSubject="Product 1" \
        -Dversion=1.0-SNAPSHOT
    [...]

